reviewText: I have been working out with Margaret Richard when I was only in my 30's and I am still working out with her. Now, I am in my 70's and I am still working out with her.

I loved her tapes when she was on VHS because the music was so enthusiastic. This CD is without music, and
her old tapes had all her friends there with her, and getting to know them, and feeling you were a part of the
whole show made you want to show up every day. this new one has no music, no friends, and the good
thing about it is that it is less time consuming, and you get a list of the work out to be done each day.
I have exercise with her for years and I love all of her exercises excellent videos need more
Can't do most of the exercises because the disc skips so badly.  Almost useless product.

I ordered series 19, received series 20. one episode skips, one starts with third exercise. The bodyelectric site had a sale two days after I ordered this and I could have gotten all of series 19 for what I paid for 8 episodes of series 20. Disappointed.
